These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-1::.
Beverage: cola, water
1. Beverage:water is on the far left or far right##3
2. Beverage:cola is on the right of Beverage:water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |
| Beverage   | water | cola |

 #################################
 
